4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to start their careers as data scientists. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Python, Pandas, and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course duration is 16 weeks with 3 classes weekly, and the maximum class size is 12 people. Upon completion, students will receive a recognized certificate. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit their website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop